# Thanos

Unified query view across Prometheus instances.

- **Upstream**: [thanos-io/thanos](https://github.com/thanos-io/thanos)
- **Downstream**: [openshift/thanos](https://github.com/openshift/thanos)

## Thanos Querier

- **Namespace**: `openshift-monitoring`
- **Kind**: Deployment (2 replicas)
- **Jsonnet**: `jsonnet/components/thanos-querier.libsonnet`
- Central query endpoint federating platform Prometheus + UWM Prometheus
- Deduplicates HA replica results
- Powers the monitoring console UI

## Thanos Ruler (UWM only)

- **Namespace**: `openshift-user-workload-monitoring`
- **Kind**: StatefulSet
- **Jsonnet**: `jsonnet/components/thanos-ruler.libsonnet`
- Evaluates user-defined alerting/recording rules

## Thanos Sidecar

- Runs within each Prometheus pod as a container
- Exposes StoreAPI for Thanos Querier to query Prometheus data
